<collectingCountry box="[714,842,877,903]" name="Madagascar" pageId="5" pageNumber="142">Madagascar</collectingCountry>
and the 
<collectingCountry box="[945,1047,877,903]" name="Comoros" pageId="5" pageNumber="142">Comores</collectingCountry>
, five of which are newly described.
</paragraph>
